INSERT INTO `locales_source` VALUES ('8268','/geriatrico/?q=admin/config/media/socialmedia/setup/1','default','Social media profiles setup','','7.43'),('8269','/geriatrico/?q=admin/config/media/socialmedia/setup/1','default','<p>The first step is to setup your social media profiles. The social media module supports several platforms such as Twitter, Facebook and Google+. If you already have accounts enter them below. If you have not setup any social media profiles yet or want to create additional ones, follow the homepage links below to create accounts. \n</p><p>\nYou do not have to create an account on all platforms. Any platforms that you do not enter a profile url for will be ignored. You can add and remove profiles later on the Social Media configuration page.  ','','7.43'),('8270','/geriatrico/?q=admin/config/media/socialmedia/setup/1','default','Save profiles','','7.43'),('8271','/geriatrico/?q=admin/config/media/socialmedia/setup/1','default','Profile information has been saved.','','7.43'),('8272','/geriatrico/?q=admin/config/media/socialmedia/setup/2','default','Social media profile widget setup','','7.43'),('8273','/geriatrico/?q=admin/config/media/socialmedia/setup/2','default','Social media profile widget','','7.43'),('8274','/geriatrico/?q=admin/config/media/socialmedia/setup/2','default','The profile widget provides a set of buttons that link to your social profiles. Check each platform you want displayed in your default profile widget set. You can edit and change the sort order later.','','7.43'),('8275','/geriatrico/?q=admin/config/media/socialmedia/setup/2','default','visit the profile settings page','','7.43'),('8276','/geriatrico/?q=admin/config/media/socialmedia/setup/2','default','visit the profile widget set configuration page','','7.43'),('8277','/geriatrico/?q=admin/config/media/socialmedia/setup/2','default','Only platforms that you have entered profile information for can be enabled. To enable additional profiles, !profiles_link. To place t